            "bestRating": "5",
            "worstRating": "1"
          },
          "reviewBody": "It's been 6 years with this institution and the dedication of urs teachers is indeed exemplary. Providing one of the best infrastructure in the city, the school stands out in its impressive structure and co curricular activities.",
          "publisher": {
            "@type": "Organization",
            "name": "Yellow Slate"
          }
        },
        {
          "@type": "Review",
          "itemReviewed": {
            "@type": "School",
            "name": "The Newtown School - Newtown"
          },
          "author": {
            "@type": "Person",
            "name": "esna nath"
          },
          "datePublished": "2024-12-25",
          "reviewRating": {
            "@type": "Rating",
            "ratingValue": "5",
            "bestRating": "5",
            "worstRating": "1"
          },
          "reviewBody": "The Newtown School is a shining example of what a top-tier educational institution should be. The school’s academics are exceptionally strong, with a well-rounded curriculum designed to engage students at all levels. The teaching staff is dedicated, knowledgeable, and committed to fostering an environment where students can thrive both intellectually and personally. Teachers go above and beyond to ensure every child receives the attention they need to excel.\n\nIn terms of infrastructure, the school is truly impressive. Classrooms are spacious, modern, and equipped with state-of-the-art technology that enhances the learning experience. The library is well-stocked with a diverse range of books and digital resources, making it a hub for students to explore and learn. Science and computer labs are cutting-edge, ensuring that students get hands-on experience with the latest tools and technologies.\n\nThe school offers excellent sports facilities, art studios, and performance spaces, allowing students to explore and nurture their extracurricular interests. The emphasis on holistic development means that every student can find their passion, be it in academics, sports, or the arts.\n\nAs for the future, this school is well on its way to becoming one of the best-decorated institutions in the region. With continuous investment in both academic and extracurricular programs, the school is set to become a leader in educational excellence. The strong foundation in both teaching quality and infrastructure ensures that it will remain at the forefront of education for years to come.\n\nHighly recommended!",
          "publisher": {
            "@type": "Organization",
            "name": "Yellow Slate"
          }
        },
        {
          "@type": "Review",
          "itemReviewed": {
            "@type": "School",
            "name": "The Newtown School - Newtown"
          },
          "author": {
            "@type": "Person",
            "name": "Souvik Kar"
          },
          "datePublished": "2024-12-25",
          "reviewRating": {
            "@type": "Rating",
            "ratingValue": "5",
            "bestRating": "5",
            "worstRating": "1"
          },
          "reviewBody": "Spent 6 years in this beautiful organization. It has become a part of my existence now. Top notch infrastructure, an amicable teaching environment, vast scope for co-curricular and extra-curricular activities and gifted teachers are some of the many brownie points of New Town School.",
          "publisher": {
            "@type": "Organization",
            "name": "Yellow Slate"
          }
        },
        {
          "@type": "Review",
          "itemReviewed": {
            "@type": "School",
            "name": "The Newtown School - Newtown"
          },
          "author": {
            "@type": "Person",
            "name": "Best chess player for nts"
          },
          "datePublished": "2024-12-14",
          "reviewRating": {
            "@type": "Rating",
            "ratingValue": "5",
            "bestRating": "5",
            "worstRating": "1"
          },
          "reviewBody": "As an ex student I feel the school has never caused any discrepancy in terms of quality education. The teachers are helpful, caring and even motivate you to score even if you aren't a bright student. I have seen improvement with my own eyes. However after 2018 and lockdown the school's vibe and charm was lost. The number of events and opportunities was reduced to some extent. There were problems with the management. However today I feel the school is recovering quickly and is ready to carve its name once again in the hearts of the children and parents alike.",
          "publisher": {
            "@type": "Organization",
            "name": "Yellow Slate"
          }
        },
        {
          "@type": "Review",
          "itemReviewed": {
            "@type": "School",
            "name": "The Newtown School - Newtown"
          },
          "author": {
            "@type": "Person",
            "name": "KOUSANI GHOSH"
          },
          "datePublished": "2024-12-12",
          "reviewRating": {
            "@type": "Rating",
            "ratingValue": "5",
            "bestRating": "5",
            "worstRating": "1"
          },
          "reviewBody": "Exceptional School with Outstanding Facilities!\n\nI am thoroughly impressed with the school's exceptional infrastructure, designed specifically with children in mind. The campus boasts:\n\n- Stunning, child-friendly architecture\n- Efficient and experienced faculty\n- Reliable, flawless bus service\n- Fully air-conditioned classrooms, halls, and central areas\n- Exciting indoor play areas and outdoor sports facilities, including basketball courts\n\nThe school's attention to detail and commitment to providing a comfortable, secure, and engaging environment for students is truly commendable. Highly recommended!",
          "publisher": {
            "@type": "Organization",
            "name": "Yellow Slate"
          }
        },
        {
          "@type": "Review",
          "itemReviewed": {
            "@type": "School",
