          },
          "datePublished": "2024-12-10",
          "reviewRating": {
            "@type": "Rating",
            "ratingValue": "1",
            "bestRating": "5",
            "worstRating": "1"
          },
          "reviewBody": "No principle, No Vice principle and decreasing all kind of staff worst condition of this school... No annual sports, no anual function even no good management ...finally no teaching. students are moving out day by day but school fee are increaing each year.\nParents are in trap of building structure and false facilities and turn into fool.",
          "publisher": {
            "@type": "Organization",
            "name": "Yellow Slate"
          }
        },
        {
          "@type": "Review",
          "itemReviewed": {
            "@type": "School",
            "name": "The Newtown School - Newtown"
          },
          "author": {
            "@type": "Person",
            "name": "EXO CGASDAMAN"
          },
          "datePublished": "2024-10-21",
          "reviewRating": {
            "@type": "Rating",
            "ratingValue": "1",
            "bestRating": "5",
            "worstRating": "1"
          },
          "reviewBody": "It's a pathetic school.. in fact not a school but a 5 star facility where the emphasis is in having a 5 star facility but 1 star standard of education. If your child is scoring 96% marks, then they might teach him how to improve to 97%, but if your child is average say 60% this pathetic school will bring it down and not enhance. The teachers have no interest in their students. They are not teaching, they are doing a job 9 to 5. There's no inclination to even find out what the student has learned and what he or she hasn't. They will charge you a bomb every month without no return. I had to shift my elder son to KV and younger to APS because of this pathetic and useless school having a useless management and pathetic teachers. Pls don't waste money on this school, there are a lot of better schools in salt lake..\n\nMost of the good reviews that are written favouring the school are by employees or teachers and parents who are teachers or known to some teachers. The school is also doing cheap politics by asking few parents to write good reviews to improve the image of the school. If someone wants to see how pathetic the school is.. pls go and visit the school and see for urself. This school is on the verge of collapse and will collapse very soon. People who have loads of money want to waste it, pls go ahead and pay this school. Your own child will one day come and tell u to look for some other school.",
          "publisher": {
            "@type": "Organization",
            "name": "Yellow Slate"
          }
        },
        {
          "@type": "Review",
          "itemReviewed": {
            "@type": "School",
