            "ratingValue": "1",
            "bestRating": "5",
            "worstRating": "1"
          },
          "reviewBody": "Struggling to get the caution money refunded for my daughter for past 4-5 months. Sent multiple emails to school management, not even a response to the mails!!!! Whenever we called they said next week u ll get . We have moved places but never had such an experience with any school in the past to get our money back.. It's a harassment and uneaithical.",
          "publisher": {
            "@type": "Organization",
            "name": "Yellow Slate"
          }
        },
        {
